@baseUrl = https://products-api.sosoftbeds.workers.dev

### API homepage
GET {{baseUrl}}/
Accept: application/json

### HTML documentation
GET {{baseUrl}}/docs
Accept: text/html

### OpenAPI spec
GET {{baseUrl}}/openapi.json
Accept: application/json

### LLM guide
GET {{baseUrl}}/llms.txt
Accept: text/markdown

### Product sitemap
GET {{baseUrl}}/products-sitemap.xml
Accept: application/xml

### Product list
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products?page=1&limit=10
Accept: application/json

### Product detail by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/60cm-ottoman-bed
Accept: application/json

### Natural-language search
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/search?q=king%20size%20ottoman%20beds%20under%20500
Accept: application/json

### Configured price from selected option values
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/60cm-ottoman-bed/price?values=134102
Accept: application/json

### Categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Accept: application/json

### Content pages
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/content-pages
Accept: application/json

### Content page by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/content-pages/choose-your-adjustable-bed
Accept: application/json